body_html:
That freeze_graph error seems to indicate that you're using an older version of TensorFlow to load the graph, where 'DenseToDenseSetOperation' was still in contrib?

We should catch this error case (loading a GraphDef file that was created by a newer version of the framework) earlier. I filed #6120 to track that work.

That freeze_graph error seems to indicate that you're using an older version of TensorFlow to load the graph, where 'DenseToDenseSetOperation' was still in contrib?

We should catch this error case (loading a GraphDef file that was created by a newer version of the framework) earlier. I filed #6120 to track that work.
